1. Executive Summary

AirportFaster is a global premium airport services platform designed to aggregate and standardize airport hospitality and airport assistance services into a single technology-enabled ecosystem.

The platform will initially focus on:

* Fast Track services
* Meet & Greet services
* Lounge access booking

AirportFaster is positioned as:

A global premium airport experience platform.

The platform is not positioned as a travel agency or airport transfer company. Instead, it is designed as scalable airport infrastructure that connects travelers, suppliers, and premium airport services through a unified booking and operations platform.

